<div id="review_1384483721" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/1384483721" />
    <a title="M.F. Moonzajer" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/4153040-m-f-moonzajer"><img alt="M.F. Moonzajer" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1442880899p2/4153040.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/1384483721?book_show_action=true">Sep 06, 2015</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="M.F. Moonzajer" class="user" itemprop="url" name="M.F. Moonzajer" href="/user/show/4153040-m-f-moonzajer">M.F. Moonzajer</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1384483721" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer13933256695848226992">Money and happiness by L.V. George is a scientific piece written about ways to be happy and highly effective in your life. It also looks into financial outputs because of less stress and pressure on your life, bringing more results. The book was published on 2015 through CreateSpace Independent Publishing Platform within 142 pages. <br/>The book is separated into x chapters. The first chapter looks into the understanding of the goals in your life and the change as a choice for being happy. The second</span>
  <span id="freeText13933256695848226992" style="display:none">Money and happiness by L.V. George is a scientific piece written about ways to be happy and highly effective in your life. It also looks into financial outputs because of less stress and pressure on your life, bringing more results. The book was published on 2015 through CreateSpace Independent Publishing Platform within 142 pages. <br />The book is separated into x chapters. The first chapter looks into the understanding of the goals in your life and the change as a choice for being happy. The second chapter looks into the challenges, and the indicators of being happy and methods of earning happiness, the chapter three discusses the visualization of your goals for happiness, chapter five discuss the actions required and the will for being happy. Chapter six to eight includes the economic and financial elements in regard to your happiness. <br />This book provides empirical examples and case studies and the direct interaction between the author and people- it has real life examples. <br /></span>
  <a data-text-id="13933256695848226992" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


